      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="main-hero-image">
        <img src="/images/hero1.jpg" alt="Shipping container on a trailer" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>
        Green Valley Storage provides moving services, whether for shipping containers or storage sheds, our goal is to make it simple and efficient. This site makes it easy to see services,
        view photos of work, and contact us directly.
      </p>
      <p>
        We understand that moving a container or shed can be a big project, and we are here to help make it as easy as possible. Contact us today to learn more about our services and how we can help you with your container or shed moving needs.
        Need to move a container or shed? We can help. We have experience moving containers and sheds of all sizes, and we can provide clear quotes and scheduling to make the process as smooth as possible.
        
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
